Yvonne Meusburger
| runner   =  Elitsa Kostova

Sandra Záhlavová was the defending champion, but lost in the Quarterfinals to Magda Linette.
Yvonne Meusburger won the title, defeating Elitsa Kostova in the final, 0–6, 6–2, 6–0.
